    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<!-- build time:Tue Feb 11 2020 19:01:35 GMT+0800 (GMT+08:00) --><blockquote><p>本篇文章介绍本博客，即基于Github Pages并采用Hexo框架和Next主题的博客的自制指南。</p></blockquote><a id="more"></a><h1 id="前言"><a href="#前言" class="headerlink" title="前言"></a>前言</h1><p><br>博主是个非编程类工科生，自己做博客主要是为了玩和练笔。要制作这个博客，不需要会编程，只需要了解一些简单的语法知识。网上的教程很多，但有些总有一点小错漏，让编程小白抓耳挠腮。博主在程序猿夏同学的帮助下，断断续续两天之内顺利布置好了这个博客。现在根据亲身经历写成这篇指南，一为纪念，二为反馈，希望有缘的你也能在自制博客的过程中感受到布置新家一样的乐趣。</p><h1 id="指南框架"><a href="#指南框架" class="headerlink" title="指南框架"></a>指南框架</h1><p><br>本文主要将博客自制过程分为三步：</p><ol><li><p><strong>Github Pages博客搭建</strong></p></li><li><p><strong>Next主题美化</strong></p></li><li><p><strong>Markdown博客书写</strong></p></li></ol><h1 id="Github-Pages博客搭建"><a href="#Github-Pages博客搭建" class="headerlink" title="Github Pages博客搭建"></a>Github Pages博客搭建</h1><p><br>这里需要三个东西：</p><ol><li><p>IntelliJ IDEA</p></li><li><p>Github</p></li><li><p>Hexo</p></li></ol><h2 id="IntelliJ-IDEA"><a href="#IntelliJ-IDEA" class="headerlink" title="IntelliJ IDEA"></a>IntelliJ IDEA</h2><p>IntelliJ IDEA（以下简称IDEA）是被夏同学强烈推荐的，程序猿必备的管理工具。自制博客过程中各种文件类型的代码修改，以及后面写.md的博文都可以用这个软件，手动修改任何东西都会自动保存，左边的小箭头能够指示.md文件的段落，而且界面五彩缤纷的非常友好。</p><p><img src="/2020/02/07/%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E8%87%AA%E5%88%B6%E6%8C%87%E5%8D%97/IDEA.png" alt></p><h2 id="Github"><a href="#Github" class="headerlink" title="Github"></a>Github</h2><p>Github Pages是Github提供的博客服务，在Github中创建一个特定格式的Repository，Github Pages就会将其中的内容生成一个网页，也就是自己的博客展示出来。步骤如下：</p><ol><li><p>注册Github账号，比如echoshanyushi</p></li><li><p>新建一个Repository，命名为echoshanyushi.github.io，勾选初始化一个README.md，<strong>注意必须为账号.github.io，才会被Github Pages拿去生成网页</strong></p></li><li><p>随便在README.md里面写点啥，比如“Hello World!”</p></li><li><p>打开网页：<a href="https://echoshanyushi.github.io/">https://echoshanyushi.github.io/</a>，就可以看到“Hello World!”了，自己的网页雏形，是不是很激动！</p></li></ol><p>如果直接用这个README.md来写博文也是可以的，但是这也显得太极简了吧，于是我们需要一个好看的框架来承载我们好看的心灵，哦不，好看的博客。</p><h2 id="Hexo"><a href="#Hexo" class="headerlink" title="Hexo"></a>Hexo</h2><p>Hexo是一个博客框架，它可以嵌入好看的主题，连同我们写的博文.md文件一起生成本地的.html文件，最后推给Github去生成公开网页。步骤如下：</p><ol><li><p>安装Node.js：<a href="https://nodejs.org/en/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://nodejs.org/en/</a></p></li><li><p>安装Git：<a href="https://git-scm.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://git-scm.com/</a></p></li><li><p>安装Hexo：win+R打开cmd窗口，输入<code>npm install -g hexo-cli</code>并回车</p></li><li><p>创建本地博客</p><ul><li>在E盘下创建文件夹MyBlog并打开</li><li>右键选择Git Bash Here，打开之后的路径就是(E:\MyBlog)</li><li>输入<code>hexo ini</code>将这个文件夹初始化为博客文件夹</li><li>输入<code>npm install</code>安装依赖包</li><li>输入<code>hexo g</code>或者<code>hexo generate</code>生成静态.html网页文件</li><li>输入<code>hexo s</code>或者<code>hexo server</code>将本地网页放到本地服务器<a href="http://localhost:4000/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">http://localhost:4000/</a>，打开链接可以看到Hexo默认的博客主题效果以及一篇自带的Hello World的博文</li><li>回到Git Bash，按Ctrl+C结束，此时本地服务器链接已不可访问了<br>&nbsp;</li></ul></li><li><p>修改配置文件</p><ul><li>在E盘下创建文件夹MyBlog并打开</li><li>到Github的Repository中，Clone or download对应的链接：<a href="https://github.com/echoshanyushi/echoshanyushi.github.io.git" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://github.com/echoshanyushi/echoshanyushi.github.io.git</a></li><li>用IDEA打开博客配置文件(E:\MyBlog_config.yml)</li><li>Ctrl+F找到<code># Deployment</code>，填入如下代码，<strong>注意语法很严格，type这类副键前必须是一个Tab，git这类键值前必须有一个空格</strong>，天知道Tab这个BUG我找了多久= =<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">deploy:</span><br><span class="line">  type: git</span><br><span class="line">  repository: https:&#x2F;&#x2F;github.com&#x2F;echoshanyushi&#x2F;echoshanyushi.github.io.git</span><br><span class="line">  branch: master</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ul></li><li><p>将本地博客部署到Github上</p><ul><li>回到Git Bash，输入<code>npm install hexo-deployer-git --save</code>，安装hexo-deployer-git</li><li>输入<code>hexo d</code>或者<code>hexo deploy</code></li><li>得到<code>INFO Deploy done: git</code>即为部署成功，之前Github中的README.md会被覆盖掉</li><li>打开网页：<a href="https://echoshanyushi.github.io/">https://echoshanyushi.github.io/</a>，就可以看到之前本地服务器所看到的博客，大功告成！<br>&nbsp;</li></ul></li><li><p>发布博文流程</p><ul><li>在MyBlog文件夹中选择Git Bash</li><li>输入<code>hexo n &quot;My First Post&quot;</code>或者<code>hexo new &quot;My First Post&quot;</code></li><li>在(E:\MyBlog\source_posts)路径下，会有一个My-First-Post.md的博文文件，编辑这个文件并保存</li><li>输入<code>hexo s</code>，查看本地博客效果，按Ctrl+C结束</li><li>输入<code>hexo cl</code>或者<code>hexo clean</code>，清空生成过的静态.html文件和缓存数据，比如(E:\MyBlog\public)文件夹就没有了</li><li>输入<code>hexo g</code>，生成新的静态.html文件</li><li>输入<code>hexo d</code>，部署到Github上</li><li>打开网页：<a href="https://echoshanyushi.github.io/">https://echoshanyushi.github.io/</a>，查看更新后的博客</li></ul></li></ol><p>至此Github Pages博客搭建就完成了，但此时的博客界面非常简单，并不是很好看也没有个性化，因此接下来进入Next主题美化部分。</p><h1 id="Next主题美化"><a href="#Next主题美化" class="headerlink" title="Next主题美化"></a>Next主题美化</h1><p><br>这里开始就都是一些琐碎的设置了，主要为修改<strong>博客配置文件</strong>(E:\MyBlog_config.yml)和<strong>主题配置文件</strong>(E:\MyBlog\themes\next_config.yml)以及其他文件，所有文件的根目录都在(E:\MyBlog)下，根据个人喜好进行个性化的博客主题美化。博主采用的是Next主题，本博客的主题配置步骤如下：</p><ol><li><p>克隆Next主题，回到Git Bash，输入<code>git clone https://github.com/iissnan/hexo-theme-next themes/next</code>，此时themes文件夹下面就有一个next文件夹了</p></li><li><p>设置博客主题为Next主题</p><ul><li>打开<strong>博客配置文件</strong>，Ctrl+F找到<code>theme: landscape</code>，改为<code>theme: next</code></li><li>回到Git Bash，输入<code>hexo s</code>，就可以查看Next主题效果，按Ctrl+C结束，<strong>此后每次更改一个小地方，都建议如此查看一次，以查看效果，并及时发现错误</strong><br>&nbsp;</li></ul></li><li><p>设置基本信息</p><ul><li>打开<strong>博客配置文件</strong>，找到<code># Site</code>，修改如下：<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">title: Echo&#39;s Blog</span><br><span class="line">subtitle: 知行合一</span><br><span class="line">description: &quot;灵魂的自由是第一自由。&lt;br&gt;——李红旗&quot;</span><br><span class="line">keywords:</span><br><span class="line">author: Echo Shan Yushi</span><br><span class="line">language: en</span><br><span class="line">timezone: &#39;&#39;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ul><li>找到<code># URL</code>，设置为自己的博客网址，<code>url: https://echoshanyushi.github.io</code><br>&nbsp;</li></ul></li></ul></li><li><p>设置Next主题风格为Gemini，Next总共四种风格，我选的是Gemini</p><ul><li>打开<strong>主题配置文件</strong>，找到<code>scheme: Gemini</code>，去掉前面的注释符号#，在未选的主题前加上#<br>&nbsp;</li></ul></li><li><p>设置菜单</p><ul><li>打开<strong>主题配置文件</strong>，找到<code>menu</code>，去掉所选菜单前的#，排好序</li><li><strong>注意<code>/||</code>之间没有空格</strong>，否则对应菜单的链接将多一个%20以至于打不开，天知道这个BUG我又找了多久= =</li><li><code>home: || home</code>中的第一个home代表的是菜单的名称，后一个则代表图标的名字，在图标库<a href="https://fontawesome.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Font Awesome</a>中找到自己喜欢的图标，把名字复制过来即可<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">menu:</span><br><span class="line">  home: &#x2F;|| home</span><br><span class="line">  archives: &#x2F;archives&#x2F;|| archive</span><br><span class="line">  categories: &#x2F;categories&#x2F;|| th</span><br><span class="line">  tags: &#x2F;tags&#x2F;|| tags</span><br><span class="line">  about: &#x2F;about&#x2F;|| heart</span><br><span class="line">  #schedule: &#x2F;schedule&#x2F;|| calendar</span><br><span class="line">  #sitemap: &#x2F;sitemap.xml|| sitemap</span><br><span class="line">  #commonweal: &#x2F;404&#x2F;|| heartbeat</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ul></li><li><p>设置菜单模块，home和archives模块的链接已经自带做好了，接下来要设置另外三个</p><ul><li>回到Gui Bash，分别输入<code>hexo new page categories</code>，<code>hexo new page tages</code>，<code>hexo new page about</code>，在source文件夹下就出现了categories，tages，about三个文件夹</li><li>打开三个文件夹下的对应.md文件，在日期下分别添加<code>type: categories</code>，<code>type: tags</code>，<code>type: about</code>，其中about.md文件的正文中可以自由发挥，作为自己的简介</li><li>此时建议查看本地博客的效果，尝试点击菜单栏是否可以进入对应的页面</li><li>若成功，则以后新建博文之后，在.md文件的上方添加<code>categories: 分类1</code>，<code>tags: 标签1</code>或<code>tags: [标签1, 标签1]</code>就可以将博文自动归入对应的分类和添加对应的标签了<br>&nbsp;</li></ul></li><li><p>添加搜索功能</p><ul><li>回到Git Bash，输入<code>npm install hexo-generator-searchdb --save</code>，安装hexo-generator-searchdb</li><li>打开<strong>博客配置文件</strong>，找到<code>Extensions</code>，在下面添加：<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">search:</span><br><span class="line">  path: search.xml</span><br><span class="line">  field: post</span><br><span class="line">  format: html</span><br><span class="line">  limit: 10000</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ul><li>打开<strong>主题配置文件</strong>，找到<code>Extensions</code>，将<code>enable</code>设置为<code>true</code><br>&nbsp;</li></ul></li></ul></li><li><p>侧栏设置</p><ul><li>打开<strong>主题配置文件</strong>，找到<code># Sidebar Settings</code>，设置社交网站链接，<code>||</code>前为链接，后为图标<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">social:</span><br><span class="line">  GitHub: https:&#x2F;&#x2F;github.com&#x2F;echoshanyushi || github</span><br><span class="line">  Instagram: https:&#x2F;&#x2F;instagram.com&#x2F;echo_shan1949 || instagram</span><br><span class="line">  Zhihu: http:&#x2F;&#x2F;www.zhihu.com&#x2F;people&#x2F;shuang-yu-shu || star</span><br><span class="line">  E-Mail: mailto:echo_shan@qq.com || envelope</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ul></li><li><p>设置头像</p><ul><li>将头像文件，如head.jpg，放入(themes/next/source/images)文件夹中</li><li>打开<strong>主题配置文件</strong>，找到<code># Sidebar Avatar</code>，设置为<code>avatar: /images/head.jpg</code><br>&nbsp;</li></ul></li><li><p>设置RSS</p><ul><li>回到Git Bash，输入<code>npm install hexo-generator-feed --save</code>，安装hexo-generator-feed</li><li>打开<strong>博客配置文件</strong>，找到<code>Extensions</code>下面的<code># RSS订阅</code>，在下面添加：<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">plugins: hexo-generator-feed</span><br><span class="line">feed:</span><br><span class="line">  type: atom</span><br><span class="line">  path: atom.xml</span><br><span class="line">  limit: 20</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li>配置博客并部署完成之后，点击博客页面的RSS图标进入网页<a href="https://echoshanyushi.github.io/atom.xml">https://echoshanyushi.github.io/atom.xml</a>，该路径即为RSS订阅源路径<br>&nbsp;</li></ul></li><li><p>设置网站缩略图标</p><ul><li>将缩略图文件，如sun.jpg，放入(themes/next/source/images)文件夹中</li><li>打开<strong>主题配置文件</strong>，找到<code>favicon:</code>，设置为:<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">favicon:</span><br><span class="line">  small: &#x2F;images&#x2F;sun.png</span><br><span class="line">  medium: &#x2F;images&#x2F;sun.png</span><br><span class="line">  apple_touch_icon: &#x2F;images&#x2F;sun.png</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ul></li><li><p>设置动态背景</p><ul><li>打开<strong>主题配置文件</strong>，找到<code>canvas_nest:</code>，设置为:<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">canvas_nest:</span><br><span class="line">  onmobile: true # display on mobile or not</span><br><span class="line">  color: &quot;0,0,0&quot; # 线条颜色，三个数字分别为(R,G,B)</span><br><span class="line">  opacity: 0.5 # 线条透明度（0~1）</span><br><span class="line">  zIndex: -1 # 背景的z-index属性</span><br><span class="line">  count: 99 # 线条的总数量</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ul></li><li><p>设置顶部进度条，默认的蓝色进度条我觉得和背景不搭，而且宽度不够遮住顶部的黑线，所以强迫症还修改了一下进度条的颜色和宽度</p><ul><li>打开<strong>主题配置文件</strong>，找到<code>pace:</code>，去掉所选主题前的#，设置为:<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">pace: true</span><br><span class="line">pace_theme: pace-theme-minimal</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li>打开(themes\next\source\lib\pace)文件夹，打开所选的进度条文件pace-theme-minimal.min.css，拖到一行的最后，设置为：</li><li>修改背景为<code>background:#eeeeee;</code>，高度为<code>height:3px</code><br>&nbsp;</li></ul></li><li><p>设置底部作者图标</p><ul><li>打开<strong>主题配置文件</strong>，找到<code>footer:</code>下面的<code>icon:</code>，设置为:<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"># Icon between year and copyright info.</span><br><span class="line">icon: heart</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ul></li><li><p>设置生命倒计时，一般为网站运行时间，但博主用的是到100岁的倒计时，以提醒自己珍惜光阴</p><p>-打开(themes\next\layout_partials\footer.swig)文件，找到如下代码：</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&#123;% if theme.footer.custom_text %&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ul><li>在其之上添加如下代码：<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&lt;!-- 网站运行时间的设置 --&gt;</span><br><span class="line">&lt;span id&#x3D;&quot;timeDate&quot;&gt;Loading...&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;</span><br><span class="line">&lt;span id&#x3D;&quot;times&quot;&gt;Loading...&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;</span><br><span class="line">&lt;script&gt;</span><br><span class="line">    var now &#x3D; new Date();</span><br><span class="line">    function createtime() &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        var grt&#x3D; new Date(&quot;01&#x2F;08&#x2F;2096 00:00:00&quot;);&#x2F;&#x2F;此处修改你的100岁生日</span><br><span class="line">        now.setTime(now.getTime()+250);</span><br><span class="line">        days &#x3D; (grt - now ) &#x2F; 1000 &#x2F; 60 &#x2F; 60 &#x2F; 24; dnum &#x3D; Math.floor(days);</span><br><span class="line">        hours &#x3D; (grt - now ) &#x2F; 1000 &#x2F; 60 &#x2F; 60 - (24 * dnum); hnum &#x3D; Math.floor(hours);</span><br><span class="line">        if(String(hnum).length &#x3D;&#x3D;1 )&#123;hnum &#x3D; &quot;0&quot; + hnum;&#125; minutes &#x3D; (grt - now ) &#x2F; 1000 &#x2F;60 - (24 * 60 * dnum) - (60 * hnum);</span><br><span class="line">        mnum &#x3D; Math.floor(minutes); if(String(mnum).length &#x3D;&#x3D;1 )&#123;mnum &#x3D; &quot;0&quot; + mnum;&#125;</span><br><span class="line">        seconds &#x3D; (grt - now ) &#x2F; 1000 - (24 * 60 * 60 * dnum) - (60 * 60 * hnum) - (60 * mnum);</span><br><span class="line">        snum &#x3D; Math.round(seconds); if(String(snum).length &#x3D;&#x3D;1 )&#123;snum &#x3D; &quot;0&quot; + snum;&#125;</span><br><span class="line">        document.getElementById(&quot;timeDate&quot;).innerHTML &#x3D; &quot;Time left &quot;+dnum+&quot; d &quot;;</span><br><span class="line">        document.getElementById(&quot;times&quot;).innerHTML &#x3D; hnum + &quot; h &quot; + mnum + &quot; m &quot; + snum + &quot; s&quot;;</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">setInterval(&quot;createtime()&quot;,250);</span><br><span class="line">&lt;&#x2F;script&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ul></li><li><p>设置站点访问计数</p><ul><li>打开<strong>主题配置文件</strong>，找到<code>busuanzi_count:</code>，设置为：<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">busuanzi_count:</span><br><span class="line">  # count values only if the other configs are false</span><br><span class="line">  enable: true</span><br><span class="line">  total_visitors: true</span><br><span class="line">  total_visitors_icon: user</span><br><span class="line">  total_views: true</span><br><span class="line">  total_views_icon: eye</span><br><span class="line">  # custom uv span for the whole site</span><br><span class="line">  site_uv: true</span><br><span class="line">  site_uv_header: &lt;i class&#x3D;&quot;fa fa-user&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;i&gt;</span><br><span class="line">  site_uv_footer:</span><br><span class="line">  # custom pv span for the whole site</span><br><span class="line">  site_pv: true</span><br><span class="line">  site_pv_header: &lt;i class&#x3D;&quot;fa fa-eye&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;i&gt;</span><br><span class="line">  site_pv_footer:</span><br><span class="line">  # custom pv span for one page only</span><br><span class="line">  page_pv: true</span><br><span class="line">  page_pv_header: &lt;i class&#x3D;&quot;fa fa-file-o&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;i&gt;</span><br><span class="line">  page_pv_footer:</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li>打开(themes\next\layout_third-party\analytics\busuanzi-counter.swig)文件，将<code>&lt;script async src=&quot;https://dn-lbstatics.qbox.me/busuanzi/2.3/busuanzi.pure.mini.js&quot;&gt;&lt;/script&gt;</code>修改为：<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&lt;script async src&#x3D;&quot;&#x2F;&#x2F;busuanzi.ibruce.info&#x2F;busuanzi&#x2F;2.3&#x2F;busuanzi.pure.mini.js&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;script&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li>本地博客可能会出现大额数字的情况，但是部署到Github之后就恢复正常了<br>&nbsp;</li></ul></li><li><p>设置阅读全文按钮，只需要在博文中如下代码，那么后面的部分就不在博客首页显示了</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&lt;!--more--&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>修改文章底部的#标签图标</p><ul><li>打开(themes/next/layout/_macro/post.swig)文件，搜索<code>rel=&quot;tag&quot;&gt;#</code>，将<code>#</code> 换成<code>&lt;i class=&quot;fa fa-tag&quot;&gt;&lt;/i&gt;</code><br>&nbsp;</li></ul></li><li><p>修改博文内链接文本样式</p><ul><li>打开(themes\next\source\css_common\components\post\post.styl)文件，在末尾添加如下代码：<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">.post-body p a &#123;</span><br><span class="line">  color: #0593d3;</span><br><span class="line">  border-bottom: none;</span><br><span class="line">  border-bottom: 1px solid #0593d3;</span><br><span class="line">  &amp;:hover &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    color: #fc6423;</span><br><span class="line">    border-bottom: none;</span><br><span class="line">    border-bottom: 1px solid #fc6423;</span><br><span class="line">  &#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ul></li><li><p>添加版权说明</p><ul><li>打开<strong>主题配置文件</strong>，找到<code>post_copyright:</code>，设置为：<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">post_copyright:</span><br><span class="line">  enable: true</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ul></li><li><p>优化页面访问速度，安装hexo-neat插件</p><ul><li><p>回到Git Bash，输入<code>npm install hexo-neat --save</code>，安装hexo-neat</p></li><li><p>打开<strong>博客配置文件</strong>，找到<code># Extensions</code>，在最后添加如下代码：</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"># hexo-neat</span><br><span class="line"># 博文压缩</span><br><span class="line">neat_enable: true</span><br><span class="line"># 压缩html</span><br><span class="line">neat_html:</span><br><span class="line">  enable: true</span><br><span class="line">  exclude:</span><br><span class="line"># 压缩css</span><br><span class="line">neat_css:</span><br><span class="line">  enable: true</span><br><span class="line">  exclude:</span><br><span class="line">    - &#39;**&#x2F;*.min.css&#39;</span><br><span class="line"># 压缩js</span><br><span class="line">neat_js:</span><br><span class="line">  enable: true</span><br><span class="line">  mangle: true</span><br><span class="line">  output:</span><br><span class="line">  compress:</span><br><span class="line">  exclude:</span><br><span class="line">    - &#39;**&#x2F;*.min.js&#39;</span><br><span class="line">    - &#39;**&#x2F;jquery.fancybox.pack.js&#39;</span><br><span class="line">    - &#39;**&#x2F;index.js&#39;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>博客添加图片压缩neat</p></li><li><p>hexo报错<code>Template render error: (unknown path) parseIf: expected elif, else, or endif, got end of file</code></p></li></ul></li></ol><!-- rebuild by neat -->]]></content>
    
